Contains helper functions, constants, and extensions.

Constants.swift: Store app-wide constants like URLs, colors, and font names.
Extensions.swift: Add custom methods or properties to existing types (e.g., custom color initializers).
HelperFunctions.swift: Centralize common utility functions (e.g., formatting, date manipulation).
Logger.swift: Manage app logs for debugging and production environments.

├── Constants.swift
│   ├── Extensions.swift
│   ├── HelperFunctions.swift
│   ├── CustomFonts.swift
│   ├── Logger.swift
│   └── UserDefaultsManager.swift
